xtinction as expected, due to the fact that this reddening is\nmainly due to dust. We also find that the thickness of discs increases with\nluminosity and size, and that brighter, smaller and redder galaxies have less\nround discs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2013 21:46:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
