mposite, this may have an advantage in the\nmass production of cloaking devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jun 2013 04:27:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Jul 2013 12:08:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-07"}
